high_descs: Turn around and step forward to face the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Cut the bread on the counter into slices.
Turn around and walk forward to face the fridge.
Place the knife in the fridge.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the bread on the counter.
Pick up a slice of bread on the counter.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the bread on the counter.
Cool the bread slice in the fridge and remove it.
Turn around and walk across the room to the left to face the trash can.
Place the bread slice in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Cool a bread slice plus place it in the trash can.

high_descs: Turn left, go forward a bit, turn left, go to the counter
Pick up the knife on the counter
Slice the bread on the counter
Turn left, go forward a bit, turn left, go to the fridge
Put the knife in the fridge
Turn left, go forward, turn left, go to the counter
Pick up a bread slice on the counter
Turn left, go forward a bit, turn left, go to the fridge
Put the bread slice in the microwave, start the microwave, wait, pick up the bread slice from the microwave
Turn left, go forward a bit, turn left, go forward, turn left, go forward, turn right in front of the basket
Put the bread slice in the basket
anns.task_desc: Slice a bread, put a slice into the basket

high_descs: Turn around and go to the counter across from you.
Pick up the butter knife under the bread, on the counter.
Cut the loaf of bread on the counter into slices.
Turn around and go to the refrigerator, across the kitchen.
Place the knife in the refrigerator on the top shelf, to the left of the lettuce.
Turn around and go back to the counter where the bread is, across from you.
Pick up one of the slices of bread.
Turn around and go to the refrigerator, across the room.
Place the slice of bread in the refrigerator, on the knife, wait a moment for the bread to chill, then remove the bread from the refrigerator.
Turn around and go to the garbage can, on the floor, in the left corner of the room, across from you.
Place the slice of bread in the garbage can on the floor.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold slice of bread in the garbage.
